Title: LAB-AID
About: LAB-AID (Laboratory Automated Interrogation of Data): an interactive web application for visualization of multi-level data from biological experiments.

Datasets.Name: Example data
Datasets.Description: Example experimental data in which the morphology, function and integration of dendritic spines was studied in layer 4 spiny-stellate cells from the somatosensory cortex of a mouse model of a monogenic neurodevelopmental disorder, and compared with the behaviour of neurons of wild-type mice.
